Robert Lee WILHOIT, v. W. H. HIATT, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Atlanta, Georgia. No. 13110. United States Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. April 20, 1950. No appearance entered on behalf of appellant. J. Ellis Mundy, U. S. Atty., and Harvey IT. Tisinger, Asst. U. S. Atty., Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before HUTCHESON, Chief Judge, and McCORD and WALLER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The .judgment of the lower court is affirmed.
